SAT-Obelisk is a research / educational cryptography project.

The original "obelisk" permutation and cipher have NOT undergone independent
cryptanalysis or peer review. Do not use the "obelisk" cipher to protect real
data. For real use, select a vetted backend (chacha20, aes256gcm). See
DESIGN.md, CRYPTANALYSIS.md and THREAT_MODEL.md for the full, honest status.
